# Census API Key Configuration
#
# To use live US Census Bureau data in this app, you need a free Census API key.
#
# How to get your Census API key:
# 1. Visit https://api.census.gov/data/key_signup.html
# 2. Fill out the form with your organization email
# 3. Check your email for the API key
# 4. Copy the key and paste it below
#
# For local development:
# 1. Rename this file to .Renviron (remove .example)
# 2. Replace YOUR_CENSUS_API_KEY_HERE with your actual key
# 3. Restart your R session
#
# For Shinyapps.io deployment:
# 1. Go to your app settings on shinyapps.io
# 2. Add CENSUS_API_KEY as an environment variable
# 3. Paste your key as the value
#
# For GitHub Actions deployment:
# 1. Go to repository Settings > Secrets and variables > Actions
# 2. Add a new secret named CENSUS_API_KEY
# 3. Paste your key as the value
# 4. Update deploy-shinyapps.yml to pass the secret as an environment variable

CENSUS_API_KEY=YOUR_CENSUS_API_KEY_HERE
